{"tid":614334,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇巴打想申請做2020東京奧運Volunteers?","createTime":"2018-04-02T12:23:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-16T12:15:34.000Z","uid":55142,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"1db7fd09219b2ed3daac978538eecdfd558fb8b9","tid":614334,"uid":55142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T12:23:53.000Z","msg":"每屆奧運都會請大量Volunteers 今次都唔例外<br />\n<br />\n而今次奧運又離我地咁近<br />\n<br />\n仲係連登仔咁鍾意嘅日本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   <br />\n<br />\n機會難得呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n應該幾適合讀緊大專OR黎緊讀大專嘅巴打<br />\n<br />\n到時寫上CV打下飛機都好嘛<br />\n<br />\n黎緊2018暑假會開始招募 有興趣嘅巴打可以入下面條LINK睇下D要求同簡介<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tokyo2020.org/en/get-involved/volunteer/about/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftokyo2020.org%2Fen%2Fget-involved%2Fvolunteer%2Fabout%2F&d=N8lFs%2BBFd7K%2F5w9DddVCbNibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=61a3f3ae\" target=\"_blank\">https://tokyo2020.org/en/get-involved/volunteer/about/</a>"},{"pid":"2a25060ec33a74fa53bb2095682984992e942732","tid":614334,"uid":135408,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T12:25:31.000Z","msg":"想去參賽多啲"},{"pid":"629e786e30730fbde1e5ea2f95da7defb539efd3","tid":614334,"uid":55142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T12:26:07.000Z","msg":"可以直接入呢條LINK 睇<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tokyo2020.org/jp/get-involved/volunteer/data/volunteer-summary_EN.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftokyo2020.org%2Fjp%2Fget-involved%2Fvolunteer%2Fdata%2Fvolunteer-summary_EN.pdf&d=N8lFs%2BBFd7K%2F5w9DddVCbNibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=e1fbcaaf\" target=\"_blank\">https://tokyo2020.org/jp/get-involved/volunteer/da